TITLE: Listening for Shard Messages in Discord.js
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to listen for messages from individual shards after spawning them using the ShardingManager. It logs the evaluated code and result for each shard message.
SOURCE: https://github.com/discordjs/guide/blob/main/guide/sharding/additional-information.md#2025-04-09_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
manager.spawn()
	.then(shards => {
		shards.forEach(shard => {
			shard.on('message', message => {
				console.log(`Shard[${shard.id}] : ${message._eval} : ${message._result}`);
			});
		});
	})
	.catch(console.error);
```

