TITLE: Playing Audio with Voice Connection in Discord.js
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to subscribe a voice connection to an audio player and manage the subscription. Includes timing control for unsubscribing after a delay.
SOURCE: https://github.com/discordjs/guide/blob/main/guide/voice/voice-connections.md#2025-04-09_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// Subscribe the connection to the audio player (will play audio on the voice connection)
const subscription = connection.subscribe(audioPlayer);

// subscription could be undefined if the connection is destroyed!
